{"tid":2418650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友為左食雞翼可以去到幾盡","createTime":"2021-02-22T19:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T23:10:32.000Z","uid":195986,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"d61eaf571ef78306ac3cb8e570819cb267487a0d","tid":2418650,"uid":195986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T19:43:03.000Z","msg":"事源女友喺IG見到有個雞翼放題廣告，價錢就要$250加一($275)。咁小弟而家學生哥一個因為某原因只有$600左右剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁佢爭論點係我同兄弟就成日食貴野，依家食一餐貴少少都喺到嘈。但當時同兄弟食貴野係我有少少收入既時侯，同有少少儲蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但拍拖之後大概大半年我都冇返工淨係返學，同近排都冇再食貴嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁小弟窮困唯有賣野幫補吓自己，咁賣準備賣少少野換少少錢返黎幫補吓今個月，佢就話<br />\n&ldquo;你嗰度賣咗嘢咪有錢&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;拎嚟食幾百蚊野都唔係好過份啫&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n女友話如果佢只係剩餘$600，佢都會選擇去食 $275嘅雞翼放題<br />\n<br />\n其實如果我得返$600，食餐雞翼已經得返一半錢。雖然而家唔洗真係返學，電腦上堂已經慳到，但個人得返成副身家幾百又真係好恐怖。<br />\n其實係我問題 定係佢理財問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求巴絲打指教<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mGg58r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mGg58r.jpg&h=6649a5c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0MEjqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0MEjqs.jpg&h=829fb4c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"579b0374ee655dbdb2774b33b77bfe7f85a48f47","tid":2418650,"uid":334982,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T19:44:17.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊都洗唔起，拍乜拖"},{"pid":"73df6f1a842273c66a94ae505e78702419751fa2","tid":2418650,"uid":63670,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貧賤夫妻百事哀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw建議你自己買雞翼自己醃好<br />\n整俾你條女食，又平又好食<br />\n放題=on9"},{"pid":"7a6503faeb737b50aa8aece3401baf2ac1cacf1c","tid":2418650,"uid":19421,"like":14,"dislike":1,"scor